@startuml

title UC-1: Create a User Profile

|User|
    start
        :Open Studently application;

|System|
    :Display welcome/landing screen;

|User|
    :Navigate to sign-up page;

|System|
    :Display sign-up form;

|User|
    :Enter name, email, password;

|System|
    :Validate input;
    while (Input valid?) is (yes)
        :Store profile (name, email, password hash);
        note right
            Complete within 1s (95%)
            Use SHA-512 for password storage
        end note
        :Display confirmation;
        :Show Home Page;
        stop
    endwhile (no)

    :Show validation errors;
    :Show sign-up form with preserved entries;
    note right
        emphasize invalid values and focus first invalid field
    end note
    stop

@enduml